
COMMAND:
   meditate 

ART:
   meditation is a way to heal faster. The monk sits down
   in the lotus position and concentrates on her/his body.
   During meditation the monk can only do little things as
   say, mt, score, stand, monkey, monk, att, help .... 
   With wake the monk stops the meditation.

COST:
    none 

POWER:
   wisdom/skill depending
